    <h1>Neighborhood Pages</h1>
    <p class="description">Hyperlocal landing pages targeting specific neighborhoods, districts, or zip codes within a metro area. They capture high-intent local traffic that city-level content misses — turning "dentist in Houston" into "dentist in Montrose."</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
